high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the stove top, turn right, go forward, turn right at the kitchen island.
Take the knife next to the cell phone from the counter.
Move to the left a step and face the pot on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Turn right, go forward to the stove top, turn left, go forward and to the left to the right side of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the stove top, turn right, go forward, turn right at the kitchen island where the pot is.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave, take the apple from the microwave.
Turn left, go forward to the stove top, turn left, go forward and to the left to the right side of the sink.
Put the piece of apple in the sink to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around, move past the end of the kitchen island, then head right and once you pass the toaster on the counter, turn right to face the end of the island.
Pick up the sharp knife that's closest to the head of lettuce from the island.
Move a step to the left to stand directly in front of the pan on the corner of the island.
Use the knife to slice the apple to the right of the pan.
Turn right, move around the island and continue to the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink by the tomato.
Turn around and head back to the far side of the island where you left the sliced apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the island.
Turn around to face the microwave on the counter in the corner.
Place the apple slice inside and then remove once heated.
Turn left, and once you pass the end of the island, head left again to the kitchen sink.
Place the apple slice in the sink next to the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of apple in the kitchen sink.
